These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, fish, lizard, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice | soy-milk | milk |
| Pet        | hedgehog | fish   | chinchilla | lizard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, fantasy, family, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, turkish, spanish, italian
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the indian is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the spanish is in an odd position##4
4. the indian is the person watching satire movies##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the spanish##1
6. the indian is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | satire  | fantasy  | documentary |
| Nationality   | italian    | indian | spanish | turkish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, peach, tomato, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, martial-arts, fantasy, horror
1. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | zucchini | tomato | peach    | avocado      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | horror     | sports | martial-arts |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, video-games, fishing, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, soul, d&b
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the fan of jazz and the fan of d&b##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | dancing | chess | video-games | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | jazz   | salsa    | d&b  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, ambient, indie, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, egyptian, turkish, canadian
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the egyptian is the fan of blues##1
3. the turkish is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
5. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
6. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | disco    | indie   | blues       |
| Nationality   | indonesian | canadian | turkish | egyptian |

