.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, superhero, adventure, action
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, colombian, chinese, australian
1. the colombian is in an even position##4
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the colombian##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
4. the argentine is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the chinese is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | superhero | action | zombie |
| Nationality   | australian | colombian     | argentine  | chinese  |

