.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, crime, musical, thriller
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, scooter, subway, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person driving the airplane is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | thriller | musical | crime    |
| Transport     | airplane | subway  | bike     | scooter |

