.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, police-officer, musician, photographer
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
2. the photographer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the photographer##3
4. the photographer is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the lawyer is between the photographer and the police-officer##2
6. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the hamster is between the lawyer and the owner of the horse##2
8. the lawyer is on the left or right of the police-officer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | police-officer | lawyer      | photographer | musician |
| Pet   | dog  | chinchilla | hamster    | horse            |

