.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, cranberry, grapefruit, artichoke
4 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, fish, chinchilla
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person eating grapefruit##2
4. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating grapefruit is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | artichoke | cranberry   | radish | grapefruit |
| Pet    | chinchilla     | guinea-pig | lizard     | fish  |

