.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, fanta, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, hip-hop, punk, r&b
1. the person drinking milk is the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of r&b is between the fan of pop and the person drinking fanta##2
4. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | fanta   | milk | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | punk | hip-hop | r&b        | pop    |

