.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, iced-tea, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, tennis, surfing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | coffee   | soy-milk      | iced-tea      |
| Sport      | tennis | surfing | rowing | skiing |

