.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, strawberry, pear, blueberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, indie, trance, pop
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of country##1
2. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
3. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pear is between the fan of indie and the fan of trance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | blueberry | strawberry  | pear  | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | trance | country | indie   |

