.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, sudoku, fishing, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, basketball, biathlon, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | collecting | sudoku         | video-games   | fishing |
| Sport   | biathlon    | basketball | swimming | surfing   |

