.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, video-games, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, parkour, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | gardening | hiking | video-games    | photography |
| Sport   | surfing   | volleyball  | weightlifting | parkour     |

