.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, writing, baking, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: french, pakistani, colombian, dutch
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
3. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the colombian is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the pakistani is between the dutch and the colombian##2
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | baking | dancing | writing    |
| Nationality   | colombian | pakistani  | dutch     | french |

