.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, cola, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, eggplant, asparagus, cabbage
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
7. the person eating pumpkin is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk    | cola       | mirinda |
| Food       | eggplant  | asparagus | cabbage | pumpkin  |

