.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, spanish, egyptian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, ship, bike
1. the australian is on the left of the polish##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the egyptian##1
5. the australian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | egyptian | australian  | polish |
| Transport     | quad-bike      | ship       | train | bike     |

