.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, doctor, mechanic, dressmaker
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, ship, airplane
1. the doctor is in an even position##4
2. the doctor is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
3. the person driving the scooter is between the chef and the person driving the roller##2
4. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the dressmaker##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | chef | mechanic   | dressmaker | doctor |
| Transport   | airplane          | scooter | roller         | ship  |

 